snippet.title: HAWKED - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
HAWKED is an online PvPvE extraction shooter coming soon to PC and consoles. Squad up to explore a mysterious island, battle monsters, outwit enemy players to steal ancient treasures, and get the hell outta there. Visit 
https://playhawked.com
and sign up for the Closed Alpha (November 24–28) now!

Join the HAWKED Community:
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/mrbqB7sJpJ
Twitter: https://twitter.com/PlayHAWKED
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/playhawked/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/HAWKEDGame
